prompt: ग्राहक सेवा का मुख्य उद्देश्य ग्राहकों की समस्याएँ पहचानकर उनका समाधान जल्दी और स्पष्ट तरीके से करना है। इसमें ऑर्डर की स्थिति बताना, रिटर्न और रिफंड प्रोसेस करना, गलत या खराब प्रोडक्ट की शिकायत संभालना, डिलीवरी में देरी की जानकारी देना, और वारंटी से जुड़ी सहायता प्रदान करना शामिल है। अच्छी ग्राहक सेवा ग्राहक के अनुभव को बेहतर बनाती है, ब्रांड पर भरोसा बढ़ाती है, और लंबे समय के संबंध बनाने में मदद करती है।
output: The main objective of customer service is to identify customer problems and resolve them quickly and clearly. It includes reporting order status, processing returns and refunds, handling complaints of incorrect or defective products, informing of delays in delivery, and providing warranty-related support. Good customer service improves the customer experience, builds brand trust, and helps build long-term relationships.

prompt: Summarize the following customer service conversation. Focus on the customer's issue, agent's response, resolution offered, and any constraints mentioned:  Customer:My order was supposed to arrive yesterday, but nothing showed up. Tracking hasn’t updated for 3 days. What’s going on? Agent:Give me the order ID. Customer:#456-99812-AA Agent:The carrier screwed up. Package is stuck at their hub. ETA is now 2–3 days. Do you still want it, or do you want a refund? Customer:I needed it yesterday. Just cancel it. Agent:I can’t cancel while it’s in transit. The only options are:You wait and return it once delivered, or I issue a replacement now. Customer:Fine, replacement. Agent:Done. Replacement will arrive by Tuesday. You’ll get an email confirmation shortly. Customer:Will I be charged again? Agent:No. If the original package eventually shows up, reject it. Customer:Okay. Agent:Anything else? Customer:No, that’s it.
output: Customer's order was supposed to arrive yesterday, but the tracking hasn't updated for 3 days. The carrier screwed up and the package is stuck at their hub. The replacement will arrive by Tuesday and the customer will get an email confirmation shortly. If the original package eventually shows up, reject it.
